  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">BreederHQ is built for rabbitries that:</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Have 20+ rabbits (or plan to)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Produce multiple litters per month</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Show rabbits (ARBA)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Track pedigrees carefully</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
