        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Need to make quick decisions with good data</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 8: Who This Is Not For -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">BreederHQ probably isn't for you if:</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>You have a few pet rabbits</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>You breed occasionally</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Cage cards handle your needs</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        No judgment. Not everyone needs software. If your current system works, keep using it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 9: FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Questions rabbitries ask</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can it handle the volume of rabbit breeding?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Built for high-volume, rapid-cycle breeding.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Does it generate pedigrees automatically?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. As you record breedings and kits, pedigrees build themselves.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I track show results?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Show records, legs, and Grand Champion status.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What about color genetics?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Genetics tracking helps with color prediction and planning.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I try it before paying?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. 14-day free trial with full access. No credit card required to start.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

